title: HOTD: Getting Off On The Wrong Foot
description:
The King is dead (spoiler), which means it's time to start a new chapter in the history of Westeros.  But House of the Dragondoesn't make things easy.  From foot fetishes to child cage matches, this episode throws all the cringy material at us, and it can only lead to one thing:  war.  And nightmares.  But mostly war.

Watch us on video with Crappens on Demand here:  https://www.patreon.com/posts/73435560?pr=true
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
